Subject: https://w3id.org/rosettastmtont/rosettastmtont.owl#symmetric
Value: 'True' indicates that the relation in the Rosetta Statement between the subject and the object that belongs to this object position is symmetric.

Subject: https://w3id.org/rosettastmtont/rosettastmtont.owl#transitive
Value: 'True' indicates that the relation in the Rosetta Statement between the subject and the object that belongs to this object position is transitive.

Subject: https://w3id.org/rosettastmtont/rosettastmtont.owl#unlisted_by
Value: \"An object property indicating the person who set the visibility of a specific Rosetta Statement to \"unlisted\". Unlisted Rosetta Statements cannot be found via the search interface of the application.\"
